I"f<h1 id="é—®é¢˜æè¿°">é—®é¢˜æè¿°</h1>
<p>Given a <strong>square</strong> array of integers <code class="highlighter-rouge">A</code>, we want the <strong>minimum</strong> sum of a falling path through <code class="highlighter-rouge">A</code>.</p>

<p>A falling path starts at any element in the first row, and chooses one element from each row.  The next rowâ€™s choice must be in a column that is different from the previous rowâ€™s column by at most one.</p>
